data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This exquisite residence is the epitome of modern elegance. Step into the open-concept living and dining space, adorned with laminate flooring throughout. The heart of this charming abode is the recently updated kitchen, featuring granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and pristine cabinets. As you explore further, you'll discover the comfort of three spacious bedrooms, providing a cozy retreat for every member of the household. But the allure doesn't end indoors – step outside into the expansive backyard, a perfect canvas for your outdoor aspirations. Whether it's entertaining guests or enjoying peaceful moments, this space is a true extension of your home. Practicality meets luxury with a newer roof, ensuring peace of mind and longevity. This property is more than a house; it's a home where memories are made and dreams are realized. A perfect starter home that seamlessly combines modern amenities with timeless charm. Sellers are motivated!
